# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   Comment in the line below if you are opt-in, or keep it commented out
#   to share the project.
#.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different OS, they may get conflicts.
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is associated with poetry and sometimes shared.
#   poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock is associated with pdm and sometimes shared.
#   pdm.lock

